<br>
I'm still waiting for credible evidence that Iraq had the WMD's which we all suspected they had, but our administration insisted <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>were</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> there.<br>
<br>
I'm still waiting for an explanation of how the very credible intelligence U.S. officials couldn't risk sharing with the American public has apparently vanished into so much smoke now that the biggest part of the war is done.<br>
<br>
I'm still waiting for our soldiers to stop dying, in ones and twos, sometimes threes and fours, every day.<br>
<br>
I'm still waiting for the U.S. to take more than a half-hearted step towards giving Iraq back to the Iraqis; but once again, with Jay Bremer cancelling a congress of prominent Iraqi figures to discuss a future government last Saturday, this doesn't look too likely in the near future.  (The congress was held, <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>without</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> U.S. supervision.)<br>
<br>
I'm still waiting for a good explanation for why we fought this war, Saddam becoming the next Hitler <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  not withstanding. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jadrax>Jadrax</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 1441<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/18/03 5:07 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grimstaff, now I'M waiting</span><hr size=1> Think we could get a seperate forum for calling out grim? ;o) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=erumaroneverbright>Erumaron Everbright</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 317<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/18/03 7:06 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grimstaff, now I'M waiting</span><hr size=1> would be 10,000 threads long! <p><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Here at graffe's...we don't care about what you say now, only what we assume you'll say later</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aurianne>Aurianne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 3731<br>