<br>
Why did we fight this war? Because Saddam was an evil fuck, and even if he doesn't have WMD, the only reason is because of the sanctions -- fact -- and we would never have been able to lift the sanctions without Saddam gone -- fact.<br>
<br>
What the fuck is so hard to understand about this? The real reason for the war, for me, in the end, had little to do with what Saddam had. It has to do with what Saddam clearly WANTED to do, WOULD do, and was only STOPPED from doing because of extreme and continued efforts by the outside world, efforts which as a necessary consequence brought great suffering to the Iraqi people. <br>
<br>
Saddam gone, sanctions lifted, Iraqi people happy, or they will be once the smoke settles. I am not happy that our troops are still there, or that they're still dying, or that it appears our government pulled a fast one over us with their specious &quot;evidence&quot;. But to claim you don't have a &quot;good explanation&quot; for why we fought this war, either means you aren't as clever as I give you credit for -- which I doubt, you're quite clever -- or you're lying. You may not agree with the reason, you may think eternal sanctions really were the way to go, but the explanation is solid and defensible, and good. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pedidustyboots>Pedi Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 966<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/18/03 11:04 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grimstaff, now I'M waiting</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.geocities.com/leopa_panthera/misc/thompson.txt"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=claudshadowflare>ClaudShadowflare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>Has Eddie Murphy's<BR>taste in women</span><br>  Posts: 3744<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/18/03 11:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Grimstaff, now I'M waiting</span><hr size=1> <!-